description: Live show filmed at With Full Force Summer Open Air on July 3, 2003.
name: Six Feet Under: Live with Full Force

review.name: a bad-ass display of death metal at its finest
review.reviewBody: this really kicked ass, and TNT being sung by Chris Barnes, it almost seems like it was written for that purpose. damn. all the songs are very well done and i was constantly offended throughout the performance, if i actually owned it i might consider buying a cheap DVD play so it would never have to leave. Even so it is an interesting sight to see six feet under playing at such a large venue compared to the usual dinge ridden holes they usually dominate. I would have liked to see them play "when skin turns blue" but you win some u lose some. Over all it was a great waist of about 50 minutes of my time and id gladly do it again, its more fun with company but check it out either way.
